every story has two sides.

6
00:00:28.542 --> 00:00:31.083
But for my mama. grandma
and me...

7
00:00:31.208 --> 00:00:33.000
there were three.

8
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:34.750
And they all led to
what would become

9
