mistake twice.

269
00:13:54.042 --> 00:13:55.875
Not now that I got Mary.

270
00:13:57.250 --> 00:13:59.625
-Is that what you think I am?

271
00:13:59.708 --> 00:14:00.917
A bad man?

272
00:14:02.875 --> 00:14:06.250
