for Veronica Bailey.

304
00:15:56.542 --> 00:15:57.500
-Coming up short?

305
00:15:58.667 --> 00:16:00.208
-Willard.

306
00:16:00.292 --> 00:16:02.083
-So you do remember my name.

307
00:16:03.708 --> 00:16:06.000
