that I can manage.

430
00:21:51.000 --> 00:21:51.958
-Mama?

431
00:21:55.125 --> 00:21:56.208
Baby brother?

432
00:21:56.333 --> 00:21:59.208
-Mm-hmm. Sure is. Mary.
This is Sammy.

433
00:21:59.292 --> 00:22:03.458
-Hi Sammy. I love him.

434
00:22:03.458 --> 00:22:05.500
-And he loves you.

435
00:22:05.542 --> 00:22:07.542
