more time there at church too.

442
00:22:22.958 --> 00:22:24.583
you wait and see. Okay?

443
00:22:26.583 --> 00:22:27.333
Yeah.

444
00:22:28.292 --> 00:22:30.792
-From me for you.

445
00:22:30.875 --> 00:22:32.458
-Aww.

446
00:22:32.458 --> 00:22:36.167
