00:23:01.375 --> 00:23:03.250
-...what. am I lying?

463
00:23:03.250 --> 00:23:04.125
-Of course you're not.

464
00:23:04.208 --> 00:23:05.125
-Willard!

465
00:23:06.792 --> 00:23:08.458
-Mary and I was just playing.

466
00:23:10.125 --> 00:23:11.375
