and Wednesday sermons.

1134
00:58:09.333 --> 00:58:10.167
[chuckles]

1135
00:58:11.125 --> 00:58:12.875
Uh... okay. I got one.

1136
00:58:12.958 --> 00:58:15.792
What do pirates
call Noah's boat?

1137
00:58:16.875 --> 00:58:18.208
The Arrrrrk.

1138
00:58:18.208 --> 00:58:20.708
[group laughing]

1139
00:58:21.708 --> 00:58:23.167
