1249
01:03:26.042 --> 01:03:27.542
It's about Jesus. right?

1250
01:03:30.042 --> 01:03:33.125
-You've got a beautiful soul.
Mary Bailey.

1251
01:03:33.208 --> 01:03:36.417
-What I got is the best
